creator: x2line
descriptionHtml:
Baby Adopter is a babysitting, nursery and dress up game for people who love to take care of little babies.

Adopt and feed a cute little baby!
Feed, buy clothes, shoes and toys and take care.

You have to feed your baby when hungry. The baby has to be with energy equivalent of 30. And do not let your baby get sick... This is the goal of Baby Adopter.

Game Locations.
Another goal is to explore and purchase items for the Baby Room, Bathroom, Playground, Playroom, Family Room, Game Center, Music Room and others. And purchase all the toys.

Egg Hunt.
Another goal is to hunt, find, collect and complete the collection of mini trophy creatures. You need to look for eggs, hunt, crack and hatch and finally own creatures which are inside the eggs. The eggs can be found randomly in different game locations. Need to wait after each crack in order to proceed with the following crack. The egg will be hatched after 3 cracks. The egg which was cracked once can be found in the same location.

Karma represents your overall game progress and player experience.
The baby will grow after 100 days of age (after acquiring clothes and shoes).

===
The baby will respond with sounds on tap on the Main screen. It is possible to change sound settings on the Account screen. The game is accessible for visually impaired and blind people (TalkBack).

===

descriptionHtml:
Baby Adopter is a babysitting, nursery and dress up game for people who love to take care of little babies.

Adopt and feed a cute little baby!
Feed, buy clothes, shoes and toys and take care.

You have to feed your baby when hungry. The baby has to be with an energy equivalent of 30. And do not let your baby get sick... This is the goal of Baby Adopter.

Game Locations.
Another goal is to explore and purchase items for the Baby Room, Bathroom, Playground, Playroom, Family Room, Game Center, Music Room and others. And purchase all the toys.

Egg Hunt.
Another goal is to hunt, find, collect and complete the collection of mini trophy creatures. You need to look for eggs, hunt, crack and hatch and finally own creatures which are inside the eggs. The eggs can be found randomly in different game locations. Need to wait after each crack in order to proceed with the following crack. The egg will be hatched after 3 cracks. The egg which was cracked once can be found in the same location.

Karma represents your overall game progress and player experience.
The baby will grow after 100 days of age (after acquiring clothes and shoes).

***
The baby will respond with sounds on tap on the Main screen. It is possible to change sound settings on the Account screen. The game is accessible for visually impaired and blind people (TalkBack).

descriptionHtml:
Discover the Heart of Virtual Parenting in Baby Adopter!

Welcome to Baby Adopter, a captivating world where babysitting meets adventure, perfect for those who revel in the joys of caring for little ones.

Begin Your Parenting Adventure:

Adopt a precious virtual baby and embark on a nurturing journey. Your mission is multifaceted: feed them, clothe them, and ensure their happiness and health. As you diligently care for your baby, you'll earn points that are vital for their growth and happiness.

Earn and Spend Points – The Cycle of Care:

In Baby Adopter, every action counts. Earn points by feeding your baby, taking care of them, engaging in the Egg Hunt, and playing exciting mini-games. Use these points to purchase adorable clothes, shoes, toys, and essential items for various locations such as the Baby Room, Playroom, and Bathroom. Filling up each game location with items is a fulfilling goal, enhancing your baby's environment and your experience.

Egg Hunt Adventure and Mini-Creatures Collection:

The Egg Hunt adds an extra layer of excitement. As you explore the game world, find and crack eggs hidden in different locations. Each egg takes three cracks to hatch, revealing a delightful mini-creature inside. Collecting these creatures is not just a goal but a joyous exploration, adding depth and fun to your gaming experience.

Engaging Mini-Games:

Supplement your babysitting journey with these engaging mini-games:

Egg Match: A lively match-3 game to test your coordination.
Free Cell: A classic solitaire card game for strategic minds.

Your Karma points reflect your dedication and progress in the game. They are a testament to your nurturing skills and virtual parenting experience.

Are you ready to step into the world of virtual childcare? Download Baby Adopter now and immerse yourself in the rewarding experience of raising a virtual child. Embrace the challenges, celebrate the milestones, and complete your collection of mini-creatures. Your adorable virtual baby is waiting for your love and care!
